  id: 23
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #6 \u2014 M\u1EB9 c\u1EE7a hai \u0111\u1EE9a
    nh\u1ECF"
  category: 3
  content: "Minh v\xE0 H\xE0 \u0111\xE3 ng\u1EE7. T\xF4i kh\xF4ng d\xE1m ng\u1EE7.
    B\xEAn ngo\xE0i ti\u1EBFng la h\xE9t ch\u01B0a d\u1EE9t. T\u1EE7 l\u1EA1nh tr\u1ED1ng,
    n\u01B0\u1EDBc c\u0169ng s\u1EAFp h\u1EBFt. N\u1EBFu ai \u0111\u1ECDc \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
    cu\u1ED1n n\xE0y, xin h\xE3y ch\u0103m s\xF3c hai con t\xF4i. Minh 7 tu\u1ED5i,
    r\u0103ng c\u1EEDa c\u1EEDa \u0111\xE3 lung lay. H\xE0 m\u1EDBi 4, hay kh\xF3c
    \u0111\xEAm. Ch\xFAng l\xE0 c\u1EA3 th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi c\u1EE7a t\xF4i. T\xF4i
    s\u1EBD c\u1ED1 s\u1ED1ng \u0111\u1EBFn c\xF9ng nh\u01B0ng n\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng..."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
